{"title":"kali安装xrdp实现Windows远程桌面连接","date":"2019-05-17T03:14:28.000Z","slug":"kali安装xrdp实现Windows远程桌面连接","updated":"2019-05-17T03:16:05.832Z","content":"<p>1.安装xrdp</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get install xrdp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2.安装vnc4server</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get install vnc4server tightvncserver</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.安装xfce4<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get install xfce4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>4.向xsession中写入xfce4-session</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">echo “xfce4-session” &gt;~/.xsession</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>5.开启xrdp服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service xrdp restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>6.Windows系统使用远程桌面mstsc访问Kali的xrdp服务</p>\n","prev":{"title":"aircrack-ng破解wep、wpa、wpa2加密的wifi","slug":"aircrack-ng破解wep、wpa、wpa2加密的wifi"},"next":{"title":"Learn to Hack","slug":"Learn-to-Hack"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/kali安装xrdp实现Windows远程桌面连接/"}